      "date": "2013-03-07 09:37:34.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n> Looks ok, but might fail testing if this version of e2fsprogs is not installed on the test nodes. Please check with Chris.\n\nAfter running loadjenkinsbuild to provision a test node on Toro cluster, I found the correct version of e2fsprogs was installed:\n\n # rpm -q e2fsprogs\n e2fsprogs-1.42.6.wc2-7.el6.x86_64",
