      "date": "2013-03-07 15:26:53.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: Looks good to me, approved\n\nWe've been exporting the \"Provides: ldiskfsprogs\" from our e2fsprogs RPM packages for quite a while already, so this should be exactly what we need to avoid getting confused by unpatched e2fsprogs with a higher version.",
